.DT 
set_skills 
Discworld living help 
set_skills 

Name
.SI 5
set_skills - Forcibly set the skills array.
.EI

Syntax
.SI 5
void set_skills(mixed *skills);
.EI

Description
.SP 5 5
This function is also known as how to annoy someone lots and lots.
Do not use it unless there is a specific thingy you wish to do, or
you have totaly munged your skills array...  This sets the skills variable
to what is passed to you.  See query_skills for a description of the
skills array format.
.EP

See also
.SP 5 5
query_skills, query_skill, query_skill_bonus
.EP
